<i>noun</i>: 수정안 [수정안], 수정 [수정], 개정 [개ː정], 개정 [개ː정], 개심 [개ː심] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>수정안 [수정안]</dt><br>
<dd>amendment</dd><br>
<dd>회의에 올려진 본래 안에서 잘못된 점을 바로잡아 고친 안.</dd><br>
<dd>An item that has been fixed from the original item that was mentioned in a meeting.</dd><br>
<dt>수정 [수정]</dt><br>
<dd>modification; amendment</dd><br>
<dd>잘못된 것을 바로잡거나 다듬어서 바르게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of correcting or refining a wrong thing so that it becomes right.</dd><br>
<dt>개정 [개ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>revision; amendment</dd><br>
<dd>글자나 글의 틀린 곳을 고쳐 바로잡음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of correcting wrong parts in lettering or writing.</dd><br>
<dt>개정 [개ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>revision; amendment</dd><br>
<dd>주로 문서의 옳지 않거나 알맞지 않은 내용을 바르게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of correcting unsuitable or wrong content in a document.</dd><br>
<dt>개심 [개ː심]</dt><br>
<dd>amendment; reform</dd><br>
<dd>잘못된 마음을 바르게 고침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of mending wrongful mindsets to be upright.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>